ygData.messageBody:
Damn, Green steels plate helm, and steels pants an such. The only things I have been able to get at lvl 16 are full bronze, Bs mantle, some ohter stuff, and 2 combine LS's. And I still have to rest forever from even a green Desert madman. Personally, I know a lot of people at low lvls with Dark Reavers and steel plate. Personally it makes me sick, they either bring up some excuse like being a smith ( and nowadays they don't earn jack), or they get things from a friend, hehe.

Dubas (mith marr)
